headline: Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) Announces US$1.51 Dividend And New Network Deal With Singleton
summary: Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) recently announced a cash dividend of $1.51 per share and entered a multi-year agreement with Singleton Associates to improve in-network access for members in Texas. These moves align with broader market trends, including a recent tech rally and an investor focus on strategic partnerships. Cigna's 14% price increase last quarter aligns with other positive market movements, suggesting these initiatives potentially added weight to the overall trajectory. Other factors such...
